OL,3,CCalls for more financial support over
OL,4,Chigh gluten-free food prices
OL,6,FJersey residents living with Coeliac
OL,7,FDisease are calling for more
OL,8,Fgovernment support and subsidies.
OL,10,FIt comes after Jersey's Food Allergy
OL,11,FConference raised awareness of the
OL,12,Fdifficulties those living with food
OL,13,Fintolerances face, with people with
OL,14,Fcoeliac disease coming forward to
OL,15,Fspeak on the financial pressures their
OL,16,Fcondition can bring.
OL,18,FKaren follows a medically prescribed
OL,19,Fgluten-free diet, explaining that
OL,20,Fsmall quantities of wheat items can
OL,21,Fhave severe consequences.
