OL,3,CCalls for more financial support over
OL,4,Chigh gluten-free food prices
OL,6,FShe says: "I usually have about 15 to
OL,7,F20-minute pockets where I will fall
OL,8,Fquite seriously ill.
OL,10,F"I suffer with a very bad, upset
OL,11,Fstomach and also severe migraines
OL,12,Fwhich will last for about two to three
OL,13,Fdays."
OL,15,FWhile Karen says she would be "lost"
OL,16,Fwithout a Jersey government subsidy
OL,17,Ffor her gluten-free shopping, she
OL,18,Fstill struggles with financial
OL,19,Fpressures.
