OL,3,CCalls for more financial support over
OL,4,Chigh gluten-free food prices
OL,6,FShe explains: "I'm absolutely thrilled
OL,7,Fthat my money's come in - it's happy
OL,8,Fdays - but it soon adds up and there
OL,9,Fit isn't a lot."
OL,11,FA recently updated Coeliac UK report
OL,12,Ffound that UK residents with coeliac
OL,13,Fdisease are paying up to 35% more for
OL,14,Fa weekly food shop suitable for a
OL,15,Fgluten-free diet.
OL,17,FThey also found that 77% of people
OL,18,Fstruggled to afford gluten-free
OL,19,Fproducts.
