OL,6,FAccording to Jersey Consumer Council
OL,7,Fstatistics, the average price for
OL,8,Fgluten-free products can double
OL,9,Fcompared to the prices of their wheat
OL,10,Fcounterparts:
OL,12,FSocial Security Minister Deputy
OL,13,FLyndsay Feltham says anyone diagnosed
OL,14,Fwith Coeliac Disease or Dermatitis
OL,15,FHerpertiformis can receive government
OL,16,Fgluten-free food subsidies.
